{"title":"搬雪","authors":["石英"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":1,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石英"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨，雪刚停下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家院里笑语喧哗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大门敞开了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要给白雪搬家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村路上千筐百担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是公社人马。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那七岁的娃娃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑提一篮雪花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那七十岁的老爷子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霜花挂上胡茬茬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看他肩挑两筐雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小步儿轻快、利洒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴里大嚷：“麦苗儿醒醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱给你请来奶妈！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}